    [-static]:
        do static VCD analysis 
    [-scale <string>]:
        the scaling factor 
    [-start_time <float>]:
        time in picoseconds at which VCD analysis starts 
    [-end_time <float>]:
        time in picoseconds at which VCD analysis ends 
    [-time_window <float>]:
        period in picoseconds for doing incremental analysis 
    [-activity_profile]:
        monitor switching activity of objects in VCD file 
    [-vcd_scope <string>]:
        the instance for VCD parsing 
    [-hinst <string>]:
        the instance in the design hierarchy corresponding to the instance in 
        the VCD selected for parsing 
    [-simvision]:
        generate SST2 database for running simvision (default false) 
    [-write_sst2 <string>]:
        SST2 database file name for viewing in other waveform viewers 
    [-nocase]:
        ignore the case for finding design objects (default false) 
    <string>:
        the name of the VCD file 
